{"tid":583834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北區交通嚴重擠塞 運輸署：避免前往或改搭鐵路","createTime":"2018-03-07T10:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T11:03:30.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc583990e1a1e84732d746bf7124e41d8cba52b","tid":583834,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"北區交通傍晚起非常擠塞，運輸署呼籲司機避免前往該區或改搭鐵路。有網民投訴，在巴士等了1小時，最後要落車步行。<br />\n<br />\n有網民就表示，「成個上水塞曬，我坐巴士已經坐左半個鐘」；「上水火車站外，附近小巴，巴士全入唔到來總站，上左車都塞死開唔出」。有網民就透露，有警員在雞嶺迴旋處指揮交通，只准巴士進出。<br />\n<br />\n因車多關係，上水一帶的路段(如雞嶺迴旋處、大頭嶺迴旋處、掃管埔路、新運路、新豐路、寶石湖路、馬會道及馬適路)的交通已十分擠塞。駕駛人士請儘量避免前往該區，或改乘鐵路前往北區。已到達該區的駕駛人士請留意並遵照警察指示，保持忍耐及密切注意電台及電視台的最新交通消息。"},{"pid":"62159e51c499555586f3d20b722bcae4d78c209f","tid":583834,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180307/_2018030718331022500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180307%2F_2018030718331022500.jpg&h=21f7470f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89bd7be47bed69a6445f5aa81a4b500bd6ae1b53","tid":583834,"uid":25858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"62159e51c499555586f3d20b722bcae4d78c209f","tid":583834,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180307/_2018030718331022500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180307%2F_2018030718331022500.jpg&h=21f7470f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6a172f69ad2ea3b42b0672b0f9a85a6f89b481","tid":583834,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T1